parameter_description: Set the amount of compression.
Sets the dynamic threshold. The higher the knob is turned up, the more sensitive Clean becomes.
Controls the loudness of the processed signal.
Controls how quickly the compression will set in.
The counter-clockwise side removes highs while the clockwise side removes lows. At noon, the EQ will have no effect.
Controls the loudness of the unprocessed signal.
If ramping is enabled, this controls the ramping speed.
Controls how quickly the compression (and left EQ mode) will fade out.
Selects the EQ mode.
Manipulates the physical behaviour of Clean's dynamic response.
Turns off/on Clean.
Engages a swell effect.
Enters/exits the Hidden Menu.
usage: 0: Exit ALT Menu; 1-127: Enter ALT Menu

parameter_description: Maxes out Clean's (dynamic) sag effect.
Sets the expression value over MIDI.
Save preset to specified slot.
Sets how quickly the noise gate will re-engage.
Sets the threshold for Clean's noise gate.
Sets how long it takes to reach full volume when Swell is engaged.
Allows you to set a custom value for the middle RELEASE position.
Lets you filter out low frequencies from the audio being used to control Clean's dynamic response.
Sets how long it takes to return to silence when Swell is engaged.
Selects which type of envelope follower Clean uses.
Selects the EQ's Shifty mode.
Lets you independently assign SPREAD to the EQ or volume-based effects (Compressor & Swell).
Toggles ramping of the Dynamics knob.
Toggles ramping of the Attack knob.
Toggles ramping of the EQ knob.
Toggles ramping of the Dry knob.
Toggles ramping of the Wet knob.
Toggles ramping of the Bounce knob.
Selects the direction of the Sweep.
Selects the polarity of the Sweep.
Splits a mono input signal into a stereo output signal.
Engages stereo processing.
Change the hold function for each footswitch from momentary to latching.
Allows you to use an external signal to trigger the compression.
Activates a noise gate that will mute the input when you're not playing.
Engages a special "motion mode" that modulates the amount of compression being applied.
Changes the function of the AUX footswitch to allow for manual swells.
Transforms the limiter inside of Clean to a distinct form of crumbly overdrive.
